1.INTRO
Our project’s name is “hitchhiking express”,basically is people can deliver their express by others’ cars.It not only resolve the problem that it’s expensive and difficult to deliver their express but also use traffic resources commendably.
The U.S. courier industry has many high and inconvenient places，in order to improve this traditional express delivery industry, we have proposed a new express delivery method based on the current popular concept of shared economy, to created a shared express delivery platform and established a "transporter" and " Transceiver "between the bond.
